// ========================================
// 14. Description/Information (No Answer)
// ========================================
::Information Block::This is just informational text with no answer expected. It serves as a separator or context provider.

// ========================================
// 15. Multiple Choice with Feedback
// ========================================
::Multiple Choice with Feedback::What is the largest ocean on Earth?{
=Pacific Ocean # Correct! The Pacific is the largest ocean.
~Atlantic Ocean # Incorrect. The Atlantic is the second largest.
~Indian Ocean # Incorrect. The Indian Ocean is smaller.
~Arctic Ocean # Incorrect. The Arctic is the smallest ocean.
}
